when you were working.

299
00:24:42,594 --> 00:24:43,434
Leave it for tomorrow.

300
00:24:44,034 --> 00:24:45,354
It's already 1:30 AM.

301
00:24:46,034 --> 00:24:48,354
You and your stomach need to sleep.

302
00:24:50,234 --> 00:24:50,994
Okay.

303
00:24:57,194 --> 00:24:57,994
Call me if you need me.

304
00:24:58,874 --> 00:25:00,474
But what about my proposal?

305
00:25:04,474 --> 00:25:05,754
May I take a look at it?

306
00:25:09,154 --> 00:25:10,514
Of course,

307
00:25:10,994 --> 00:25:12,394
