329
00:27:45,714 --> 00:27:46,714
You are so kind.

330
00:27:47,234 --> 00:27:48,354
It's just an extra bowl.

331
00:27:49,794 --> 00:27:50,714
Thank you, then.

332
00:28:04,514 --> 00:28:05,154
How is it?

333
00:28:07,394 --> 00:28:10,114
It's delicious,
and the pepper flavor is so strong.

334
00:28:13,034 --> 00:28:13,714
By the way,

335
00:28:13,872 --> 00:28:15,074
there's a new spicy duck bone shop

336
00:28:15,074 --> 00:28:16,354
at the entry of our block next door.

337
00:28:16,354 --> 00:28:16,954
It's doing great.

338
00:28:18,034 --> 00:28:19,714
Don't even think about it
before you're recovered.

339
00:28:24,234 --> 00:28:25,794
You can buy some without spice.

340
00:28:31,954 --> 00:28:32,714
Slow down.

341
00:28:39,874 --> 00:28:41,954
Bring me some when you go.

342
00:28:42,154 --> 00:28:43,674
I'll tell you my home password.

343
