you say it's bad for your throat.

381
00:30:44,834 --> 00:30:45,314
Who is it?

382
00:30:46,074 --> 00:30:48,914
Is it that fan girl
who came to record last time?

383
00:30:52,474 --> 00:30:54,394
Good for you, Yan Yue.
When did this happen?

384
00:30:54,954 --> 00:30:55,834
You remembered it wrong.

385
00:30:56,274 --> 00:30:57,114
She's my client.

386
00:30:57,194 --> 00:30:58,674
Who are you fooling?

387
00:30:58,874 --> 00:31:01,114
When have you ever cared about a client?

388
00:31:05,634 --> 00:31:07,994
I just knew you liked the mature type.

389
00:31:12,394 --> 00:31:12,794
Sit.

390
00:31:18,954 --> 00:31:22,794
Even though you two
are an idol and a fan,

391
00:31:23,234 --> 00:31:24,114
