392
00:31:24,114 --> 00:31:25,874
Do you know
how to win over a mature woman?

393
00:31:27,954 --> 00:31:28,914
What are you trying to say?

394
00:31:29,914 --> 00:31:33,514
When you found out
that she likes duck bones,

395
00:31:33,994 --> 00:31:36,394
didn't you feel something was off?

396
00:31:38,954 --> 00:31:40,554
Can you just say what you mean?

397
00:31:41,634 --> 00:31:42,674
A girl

398
00:31:42,674 --> 00:31:45,314
won't eat duck bones
in front of a guy she likes.

399
00:31:46,634 --> 00:31:47,154
Why not?

400
00:31:47,554 --> 00:31:48,434
Why not?

401
00:31:49,194 --> 00:31:52,314
Duck bones are greasy.
You have to use your hands

402
00:31:52,754 --> 00:31:53,994
and even get your face dirty.

403
00:31:54,434 --> 00:31:55,234
Can a girl allow herself

404
00:31:55,234 --> 00:31:57,794
to ruin her image
in front of someone she likes?

405
00:31:58,074 --> 00:31:58,754
Am I right?

406
00:32:00,336 --> 00:32:03,154
It's just eating food.
Don't make things up.

407
00:32:03,354 --> 00:32:04,954
There's a lot to learn here.

408
00:32:05,394 --> 00:32:07,394
Mr. Heisha, you're still too young.

409
00:32:08,114 --> 00:32:09,474
But when it comes to a relationship,

410
00:32:09,754 --> 00:32:10,754
you can't force it.

411
00:32:10,914 --> 00:32:12,194
Eye of the beholder, no?

412
00:32:13,474 --> 00:32:15,794
But a mature woman like her

413
00:32:15,794 --> 00:32:17,474
often can't resist

414
00:32:17,474 --> 00:32:18,794
the charm of a mature man like me.

415
00:32:19,314 --> 00:32:20,794
You're just too young.

416
00:32:21,074 --> 00:32:22,194
Mind your own business

417
00:32:23,034 --> 00:32:24,034
